dataList.title: Rosespanner Workshop
dataList.content: Ah... Give me a second. I think we need to call a timeout.

dataList.title: Rosespanner Workshop
dataList.content: Might be the sardine I ate this morning... My stomach is aching.

dataList.title: Rosespanner Workshop
dataList.content: Boss!
No such thing. SYNC is up next.

dataList.title: Rosespanner Workshop
dataList.content: Shrenne...!
She what?

dataList.title: Rosespanner Workshop
dataList.content: Shrenne told us something. While we're in here... don't ever use regeneration ampules no matter what...

dataList.title: Rosespanner Workshop
dataList.content: Haah... Saying that out loud... is breaching the contract, you dolt...
That so... Shrenne told you that? Why?

dataList.title: Rosespanner Workshop
dataList.content: I don't know... She said we'll see in due time...

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: Well, we have the simplest way to find out, don't we?
After fiddling with a regeneration ampule in his hand, Dongrang made a sudden move...
He quickly jabbed the ampule into the unguarded Fixer's body like a dagger.

dataList.title: Rosespanner Workshop
dataList.content: Ah...
The Fixer tried to remove the ampule, but its content had already entered the system...

dataList.title: Rosespanner Workshop
dataList.content: ...Why do you look so surprised, boss? What happens if the ampule is injected...?

dataList.title: Rosespanner Workshop
dataList.content: ...Huh, this is weird...
The Fixer's limbs began to twist in strange angles...

dataList.title: Rosespanner Workshop
dataList.content: Uwaah. Uagh.
Then some things started protruding through the flesh.
Collapsed on the floor, the Fixer tried to yell something, but failed to make any sound.
...Is it just me, or is this awfully familiar?
Please. You don't really think you're the only one who remembers that bug den, do you, Greg babe?
Resembling larvas or snails...

dataList.title: Rosespanner Workshop
dataList.content: ...Oh dear.

dataList.title: K Corp. Laboratory
dataList.content: Let's stop here. I dragged too many people into this.

dataList.title: Rosespanner Workshop
dataList.content: Well... It was my decision to take the deal for the money.

dataList.title: Rosespanner Workshop
dataList.content: Dearie me... Should've gone on a bigger spree yesterday if I knew it would come to this.
